1.4.0
 - Based on contribution from Volker Wandmaker
 - targeting the full support for RSE (Remote System Explorer, see http://www.eclipse.org/dsdp/tm/)

1.3.6
 - Support for project relative mappings (need to be tested)

1.3.5
 - Added option to synchronize team private data too (like .svn shit)
